Create, update and get tasks for the benefits, goals and also at a care plan level.
Create, update, and get tasks for benefits, goals, and care plans
Introduced in API version 56.0, this API is added to the Case Management API guide.
Make a POST request to the new /connect/careplan/care-plans/carePlanId/tasks resource.
New request body: Create Care Plan Task Input
New response body: Create Care Plan Task
